defaultAs well as targeting economic growth, an important objective of the reforms is to ensure that the governance of the SRN is providing value for money for the taxpayer. In his review of the sector, Alan Cook estimated potential efficiencies to be in the region of £200m per annum (in addition to the commitments made by the HA as part of the 2010 Spending Review).
