default projections of trends in road traffic and congestion are based on its National Transport Model (NTM). 
defaultUnder the 
defaultNTM, t
defaulthe main 
defaultfactors influencing 
defaultcar traffic (in terms of vehicle
default-
defaultmiles) are population, GDP per capital, and fuel cost. The model currently assumes that:
default–
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
